Title: 2. Stakeholders
Write-Up Text: In these people's social media posts the buzz is all about cost of living relief delivered through the latest Budget. Some of the ways of easing the pressure include a $400 electricity credit and a $650 credit for small businesses. Congratulations are sent to @JEChalmers for delivering on promises while clarifying high-income earners are the intended beneficiaries. Interested readers can learn more by following the links provided.
